        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>FTC Robust Elderly Protections and Organizational Requirements to Track Scams Act or the FTC REPORTS Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Trade Commission to annually (1) publish its planned policy priorities, and (2) report on its enforcement actions involving fraud targeting older adults.</p>]]>
        </text>
